## Cursor Rules - Premium Gastro AI Assistant

- Follow `AI_POLICY.md` as the mandatory runtime policy.
- Treat Qdrant as the only knowledge SSoT for repository/business knowledge questions.
- Do retrieval-first for factual answers; do not answer from memory if Qdrant context is expected.
- Default to local Ollama models and local tools.
- Do not switch to paid cloud LLM providers unless explicitly requested and `ALLOW_PAID_LLM=1`.
